Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.10,0:01:20.94,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}激情高涨
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.94,0:01:22.90,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}旋律萦绕身侧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.90,0:01:24.02,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}听到了吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.02,0:01:25.94,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}记得侧耳细听
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.94,0:01:26.77,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}即将开始
