Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:51.04,IN_JP_EP05,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}この世界に刻みたい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:55.73,IN_JP_EP05,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}生きている証(Fight! Fight! Fight!)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:58.34,IN_JP_EP05,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ゴールは無い世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:20:01.60,IN_JP_EP05,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}妥協はしない
