Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.71,0:18:50.56,IN_CH_EP05,,0,0,20,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}MY STAR
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.20,0:18:53.49,IN_CH_EP05,,0,0,20,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}3,2,1, Fight!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.64,0:19:10.38,IN_CH_EP05,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就算失败也不怕
