Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.69,0:19:20.68,IN_CH_EP05,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}沉迷其中 不顾一切
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.68,0:19:26.40,IN_CH_EP05,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}奏响这旋律吧
