Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.57,0:19:31.93,IN_CH_EP05,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不惜付出全部青春
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.93,0:19:34.17,IN_CH_EP05,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}想要遇见 想要遇见
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.17,0:19:38.77,IN_CH_EP05,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}那让自己满意的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.77,0:19:44.12,IN_CH_EP05,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}永远都在寻找之中
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.12,0:19:45.03,IN_CH_EP05,,0,0,20,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Starlight!
